Dear Officers of <%= @fund_request.fund_grant.organization %>,

This email is to inform you that your <%= @fund_request %> has been started, but requires further action before it will be considered submitted.

You may make changes to the fund_request here <<%= fund_request_url(@fund_request) %>>.

<%=render partial: 'fund_request_mailer/prospective_deadline', locals: { fund_request: @fund_request } %>
<%=render partial: 'fund_request_mailer/fund_tier', locals: { fund_grant: @fund_request.fund_grant } %>
When the fund request is ready for submission, any of the following may approve it here <<%= new_polymorphic_url([@fund_request, 'approval']) %>>:

<% @fund_request.users.unfulfilled.each do |user| -%>
 * <%= user.name %>
<% end -%>

<% if @fund_request.fund_grant.fund_source.contact_web -%>
More information is available here <<%= @fund_request.fund_grant.fund_source.contact_web %>>.
<% end -%>

Sincerely,

<%= @fund_request.fund_grant.fund_source.contact_name %>

